\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Imprint \'96 Tag Schema (V1)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 This document defines the core tagging structure for documents ingested into 
\f0\b Imprint
\f1\b0 .\uc0\u8232 Tags are designed to remain 
\f0\b simple, consistent, and market-linkable
\f1\b0 .\
The goal is not to perfectly structure every idea, but to provide enough metadata to connect research to 
\f0\b entities, sectors, and markets
\f1\b0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Core Tags\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 1. 
\f2\fs39 topic
\f0\fs36 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Definition
\f1\b0 \
The primary subject or mechanism the document discusses.\
A topic describes 
\f0\b what the article is about
\f1\b0 , not the investment opinion.\
Topics should be 
\f0\b specific but reusable
\f1\b0  across many documents.\

\f0\b Format
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
snake_case\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 Examples
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
ai_infrastructure\
hyperscaler_capex\
china_export_controls\
trade_policy\
consumer_credit\
enterprise_ai_adoption\
semiconductor_supply_chain\
defense_spending\
interest_rates\
energy_grid_modernization\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 Good topic rule
\f1\b0 \
Prefer 
\f0\b mechanism or domain-level descriptions
\f1\b0  rather than broad labels.\
Good:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
gpu_supply_constraints\
ai_inference_economics\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 Bad:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
ai\
technology\
markets\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 2. 
\f2\fs39 entities
\f0\fs36 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Definition
\f1\b0 \
Companies, organizations, people, or products referenced in the document.\
Entities create the main bridge between research and 
\f0\b markets
\f1\b0 .\
They are the most important tag for linking to:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 public equities\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 private companies\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 government actors\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 prediction markets\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 Format
\f1\b0 \
Array of values.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
["NVDA", "OpenAI", "Jerome Powell"]\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

