\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 3. 
\f2\fs39 sector
\f0\fs36 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Definition
\f1\b0 \
High-level classification describing the economic or industry area affected.\
Sectors provide 
\f0\b broad filtering
\f1\b0  across the research library.\
Keep the list 
\f0\b tight and stable
\f1\b0 .\

\f0\b Recommended values
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
