\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 4. 
\f2\fs39 sentiment
\f0\fs36 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Definition
\f1\b0 \
The overall directional tone of the document toward the topic or key entities.\
Sentiment is 
\f0\b not truth
\f1\b0  \'97 it reflects the author's perspective.\
Contradictory documents are expected and useful.\

\f0\b Allowed values
\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
bullish\
bearish\
neutral\
mixed\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 Examples
\f1\b0 \
Article arguing hyperscaler spending will increase demand for GPUs:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
sentiment: bullish\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 Article warning that Amazon is overspending on AI infrastructure:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
sentiment: bearish\
entities: ["AMZN"]\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 Article presenting both positive and negative arguments:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\fs26 \cf0 \
sentiment: mixed\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

